{"tid":1922582,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"nba jazz可以宣佈重建了","createTime":"2020-03-12T15:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T14:28:24.000Z","uid":173952,"like":55,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"3a56e7fb999ee22d40c1772597bcf05da930b697","tid":1922582,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"高拔和米曹<br />\n<br />\n 香港時間3月12日，據美媒體報導，繼魯迪-高拔之後，爵士隊當家後衛多諾萬-米曹也被確診患上新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n  昨天，爵士正選中鋒高拔確診新冠病毒，成為NBA第一例。同時，NBA宣佈無限期停賽。<br />\n<br />\n  今天，美媒體透露爵士當家後衛多諾萬-米曹也已經被確診患上新冠病毒。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n  據悉，爵士球員在私底下透露高拔在更衣室里非常不注意，經常去觸碰其他球員以及他們的物品。</span><br />\n<br />\n  現在，另一位爵士球員也被染上了新冠病毒。"},{"pid":"ecf9c4f77abc7dd4500025c47a7402110fb814fe","tid":1922582,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"咁大隻都中？？"},{"pid":"522e700443cb98557fc39fdd05d66ffae4a3a09b","tid":1922582,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"米曹都中左"},{"pid":"a4354ed4c60210f6b5326ed8cc3a6c88c51f719d","tid":1922582,"uid":225130,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"gobert應該變左過街老鼠，搞到猶他萬人迷中招<br />\n我諗無論咪嘈恢復到幾多成<br />\nd球迷都會支持比大約咪嘈，gobert就trade走"},{"pid":"9ca0add0a5a1c70d173a31edc6e51bc3d89b94c1","tid":1922582,"uid":7125,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"a4354ed4c60210f6b5326ed8cc3a6c88c51f719d","tid":1922582,"uid":225130,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"gobert應該變左過街老鼠，搞到猶他萬人迷中招<br />\n我諗無論咪嘈恢復到幾多成<br />\nd球迷都會支持比大約咪嘈，gobert就trade走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"Gobert要退役都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身攪到nba停賽都算 仲要肺炎之後唔知有咩後遺症"},{"pid":"6c5898959e94fb899452aa2748c587435eb7effd","tid":1922582,"uid":239525,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy"